#. <section class="sutta" id="sn35.158"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.158:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.158:0.2"
msgid "16. Nandikkhayavagga"
msgstr "16. The End of Relishing"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 158. Ajjhattaaniccanandikkhayasutta → ajjhattanandikkhayayonisosuttaṃ (bj) | nandikkhaya 3 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.158:0.3"
msgid "158. Ajjhattaaniccanandikkhayasutta"
msgstr "158. Focus, the Interior, and the End of Relishing"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli4.143"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.158:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Cakkhuṃ, bhikkhave, yoniso manasi karotha, cakkhāniccatañca yathābhūtaṃ "
"samanupassatha."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, properly attend to the eye. Truly see the impermanence of the "
"eye."

msgctxt "sn35.158:1.2"
msgid ""
"Cakkhuṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yoniso manasikaronto, cakkhāniccatañca "
"yathābhūtaṃ samanupassanto cakkhusmimpi nibbindati."
msgstr "When a mendicant does this, they become disillusioned with the eye."

msgctxt "sn35.158:1.3"
msgid "Nandikkhayā rāgakkhayo;"
msgstr "When relishing ends, greed ends. When greed ends, relishing ends."

msgctxt "sn35.158:1.4"
msgid "rāgakkhayā nandikkhayo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.158:1.5"
msgid "Nandirāgakkhayā cittaṃ suvimuttanti vuccati."
msgstr "When relishing and greed end, the mind is said to be well freed."

msgctxt "sn35.158:1.6"
msgid "Sotaṃ, bhikkhave, yoniso manasi karotha …"
msgstr "Properly attend to the ear …"

msgctxt "sn35.158:1.7"
msgid "ghānaṃ …"
msgstr "nose …"

msgctxt "sn35.158:1.8"
msgid ""
"jivhaṃ, bhikkhave, yoniso manasi karotha, jivhāniccatañca yathābhūtaṃ "
"samanupassatha."
msgstr "tongue …"

msgctxt "sn35.158:1.9"
msgid ""
"Jivhaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yoniso manasikaronto, jivhāniccatañca yathābhūtaṃ "
"samanupassanto jivhāyapi nibbindati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.158:1.10"
msgid "Nandikkhayā rāgakkhayo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.158:1.11"
msgid "rāgakkhayā nandikkhayo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.158:1.12"
msgid "Nandirāgakkhayā cittaṃ suvimuttanti vuccati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.158:1.13"
msgid "Kāyaṃ …"
msgstr "body …"

msgctxt "sn35.158:1.14"
msgid ""
"manaṃ, bhikkhave, yoniso manasi karotha, manāniccatañca yathābhūtaṃ "
"samanupassatha."
msgstr "mind. Truly see the impermanence of the mind."

msgctxt "sn35.158:1.15"
msgid ""
"Manaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yoniso manasikaronto, manāniccatañca yathābhūtaṃ "
"samanupassanto manasmimpi nibbindati."
msgstr "When a mendicant does this, they become disillusioned with the mind."

msgctxt "sn35.158:1.16"
msgid "Nandikkhayā rāgakkhayo;"
msgstr "When relishing ends, greed ends. When greed ends, relishing ends."

msgctxt "sn35.158:1.17"
msgid "rāgakkhayā nandikkhayo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.158:1.18"
msgid "Nandirāgakkhayā cittaṃ suvimuttanti vuccatī”ti."
msgstr "When relishing and greed end, the mind is said to be well freed.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.158:1.19"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
